# Joelclaw Systems Check 2026-07-10

## Summary

Flagg/Mac Studio is the working Central surface for current agent-mail, system-bus worker, Inngest, gateway Redis, and run capture health. Panda agent-mail is decommissioned. Agent session indexing into Flagg Typesense is fresh, but raw outbox backlogs are still large and NAS backup receipts are not clean.

